REM  Learn: PRINT, REM, strings, semicolons
REM ============================================

10 REM Welcome to BASIC!
20 PRINT "================================"
30 PRINT "  Welcome to Time Warp Rusted!"
40 PRINT "================================"
50 PRINT
60 PRINT "Hello, World!"
70 PRINT
80 PRINT "You can print text in quotes."
