100 PRINT "Hello"; " "; "World"; "!"
110 PRINT
120 PRINT "Use PRINT alone for blank lines."
130 PRINT
140 PRINT "REM lines are comments - they're ignored."
150 ' This is also a comment (apostrophe style)
160 PRINT "Program complete!"
170 END
